   Welcome to the world of language, languages, and linguistics.

   OPEN THE 25TH DECEMBER AND THE 1ST OF JANUARY

the Museum of Languages

   Covering nearly 170m², the Mundolingua permanent exhibition is an
   enjoyable and original destination, covering many different themes.

   OPEN 366 DAYS / YEAR (except non leap years)
   Follow the guide...
     *
     *
     *

   PreviousNext
   123

   Open 366 a year (except leap years)

A museum of language curiosities

   To view the program of our soirées, please vist the page “News and
   Events”
   News & Events
     *

A museum open to everyone!

   For Parisians and tourists, aged between 8 and 88, and all people who
   speak, with their voices or hands. Our alcoves enable each visitor to
   choose how much detail at every step. Whether you choose to go at your
   own pace (loan headphones provided to listen to videos and audio
   tapes), or a guided tour, there is something for everyone.

   You are welcome to follow our news to hear about our events
   (conferences, panels, workshops…). Enjoy your visit!

